{"tid":1145111,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Ariana Grande手機桌布是BTS柾國！　「近距離嘟嘴私照」曝光：我超愛你","createTime":"2019-05-08T13:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T04:14:31.000Z","uid":74065,"like":162,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"645a4780c8dd347ee5b2f65f73f93c021c9fe8b8","tid":1145111,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"南韓天團防彈少年團（BTS）新巡迴《LOVE YOURSELF: SPEAK YOURSELF》近日從洛杉磯開跑，更在美國享受難得的休假時光。成員柾國抽空去看了美國歌壇小天后亞莉安娜（Ariana Grande）的演唱會，亞莉安娜更貼出兩人在後台的近距離合照，讓粉絲大喊：「不知道要羨慕哪一個！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4065/d4065451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4065%2Fd4065451.jpg&h=e46f5256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團在美國拿下告示牌音樂獎最佳團體後，在洛杉磯連開兩場演唱會。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團在7萬人的洛杉磯「玫瑰盃球場」連開兩場，共計14萬人創下南韓歌手在美國單場動員最多人數的紀錄。在結束洛杉磯演唱後，他們也有一小段假期，成員們各自去看球賽、電影和遊樂場，享受難得的休假。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4080/d4080849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4080%2Fd4080849.jpg&h=4f283c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BTS柾國去看亞莉安娜演唱會，並在後來與她合照。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n成員柾國則去看了亞莉安娜的演唱會，並在推特用英文寫下：「在看了她的演出後，我感到和學習到很多。我受到她舞台演出的激勵，以後會更努力。」亞莉安娜則在IG貼出兩人在後台的近距離貼身合照，寫下：「尖叫！柾國，非常謝謝你來我的演唱會，這對我很有意義，我超愛你！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4080/d4080851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4080%2Fd4080851.jpg&h=8bb63381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲亞莉安娜把手機桌布設成與BTS柾國合照。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n亞莉安娜更把這張照片設成手機桌布，放上IG限時動態，讓粉絲大喊：「不知道要羨慕哪一個！」<span style=\"color: red;\">此外，由於亞莉安娜原文寫道「love u sm」，讓許多粉絲會錯意，在下面回覆：「他不是SM的藝人，是Bighit的。」但也馬上有網友跳出來解釋，那是「love u so much」的意思。</span>"},{"pid":"032ba4e97b96ffb429631886979d8a53b891893c","tid":1145111,"uid":208486,"like":55,"dislike":13,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"ariana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a558d11e7681864cc1e5b343e437f2e23c6f57","tid":1145111,"uid":152432,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"032ba4e97b96ffb429631886979d8a53b891893c","tid":1145111,"uid":208486,"like":55,"dislike":13,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"ariana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"放過個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2635869eaa9f8e0489b4c7522878dac64be6c89","tid":1145111,"uid":139671,"like":166,"dislike":20,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"Bts又成功帶紅亞莉安娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bfeccd15a3f14ce7f896a8888685a968577861","tid":1145111,"uid":208486,"like":118,"dislike":3,"score":115,"quote":{"pid":"15a558d11e7681864cc1e5b343e437f2e23c6f57","tid":1145111,"uid":152432,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"032ba4e97b96ffb429631886979d8a53b891893c","tid":1145111,"uid":208486,"like":55,"dislike":13,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"ariana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"放過個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"牙A其實幾淫<br />\n又單眼又嘟嘴<br />\n之前又喺twitter講自己條ex好大"},{"pid":"696bd789586b3718fa56dff3961bd1dd8b9909b5","tid":1145111,"uid":46435,"like":54,"dislike":13,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"發現jungcock多數食d唱歌勁既女孩子 e.g alien grenade,momo.."},{"pid":"e8c45301497a47971f66c76278c9fed731183eba","tid":1145111,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"696